Itâ€™s been ages since knowledge has been passed on from one generation to the next. Today, as well people are well aware of the fact that they must integrate knowledge into the institutions that serve them. Knowledge and science has been seen as two different factors but both come under the criteria of correlation; thus making them to work on vice-versa basis. I must say that partnerships are a vital part of any strategy that we must adopt in together seeking imaginative, innovative, and perhaps unexpected solutions.








